Definition.WordDefinition: Anthropologic \An`thro*po*log"ic\, Anthropological \An`thro*po*log"ic*al\, a. Pertaining to anthropology; belonging to the nature of man. ``Anthropologic wisdom.'' --Kingsley. -- {An`thro*po*log"ic*al*ly}, adv. [1913 Webster]
